@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (((v0 + 0.58 + v0 + 0.69) + (tmp + 0.71 - v0 + 0.98)) - (wp.exp(v1 + 0.15) + v1))
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.sin(wp.cos(v0 + 0.37)))
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.exp(0.33))
    tmp = v2
    tmp = wp.cos(0.17)
    v2 = wp.cos(tmp)
    data[tid] = v0
